	  {{ "'" + (TableQNTB.newRow.ten_quan_nhan || '') + "'" }},
	  {{ "'" + (TableQNTB.newRow.quan_ham || '') + "'" }},
	  {{ "'" + (TableQNTB.newRow.chuc_vu || '') + "'" }},
	  {{ "'" + (TableQNTB.newRow.so_dien_thoai || '') + "'" }},
    (SELECT id FROM public.don_vi WHERE ten_don_vi = {{ "'" + (TableQNTB.newRow.ten_don_vi|| '') + "'" }} LIMIT 1)
